node.title: Kitchen worker at Auckland rest home believed to have Omicron
node.description: An Auckland rest home kitchen worker is believed to have Omicron.
node.content:
["An Auckland rest home kitchen worker is believed to have Omicron.", "", "
\nPhoto: AFP\n
", "The Ministry of Health suspects the Covid-19 positive worker has been carrying the variant.", "Summerset by the Park Flat Bush is listed on its website as a location of interest.", "Management say they found out on Saturday night.", "The village and care centre is now closed to visitors, and residents have been asked to stay in their homes or rooms while a public health team does surveillance testing.", "All staff are fully vaccinated, and those who worked with the infected person are isolating and being tested."]
